<h5>The Rise of Games in the East (1985-1995)</h5>
<p>Three historical events:</p>
<ul>
<li>Legend of Zelda is created (1987)</li>
<li>In 1989, the Gameboy is created.</li>
<li>The card game Solitare was made into a video game, 1990.</li>
</ul>
